    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.85 + (0.75 * wp.abs(v1 + 0.28)))
    tmp = wp.exp(v0)
    v2 = (((v0 + 0.74 - tmp + 0.41) * 0.25) * v1)
    tmp = wp.sin(v2)
    tmp = ((0.75 + (v1 + 0.38 - v0 + 0.09)) / ((tmp + 0.76 / v2 + 0.51) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.49)))
    v0 = wp.sin(tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
